Class GymFlipFitGymOwnerRestController

java.lang.Object
com.flipfit.resources.GymFlipFitGymOwnerRestController
@Path("/gymowner") @Produces("application/json") @Consumes("application/json") public class GymFlipFitGymOwnerRestController extends Object
REST controller for gym owner-related operations. It provides endpoints for adding gym centers, viewing details, and editing profiles.
